唔貴"},{"pid":"8efc7ac3a3a3bf59bf9224cfac1ac82a23e518b1","tid":498460,"uid":85819,"like":1,"dislike":18,"score":-17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T01:20:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8201ba2a959c677a5380a216f0d897f0d3faac81","tid":498460,"uid":146205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T07:27:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用咗半年，十分好用，好順，聽歌正，影相廣角無得輸，係抵出既</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> thanks"},{"pid":"96b4020f451ca5611abb4244f270c15242b72cc5","tid":498460,"uid":46551,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T07:30:54.000Z","msg":"跟隊問   想換sony xz 或者lg v30   邊部好d <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13dfc01e112179dc0c899b7a5f0dba1f9a1e7dca","tid":498460,"uid":146205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T07:31:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>3k 用s821 cpu, 你不如睇下類似價位用s835既機好過</blockquote><br />\n不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 除左Crystal X 同G6之外都無咩機吸引到我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbtw thanks<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b31cf8a6f38fd3e7509e58f39371348924b0ae3c","tid":498460,"uid":23677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T07:32:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>3k 用s821 cpu, 你不如睇下類似價位用s835既機好過</blockquote><br />\n不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 除左Crystal X 同G6之外都無咩機吸引到我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbtw thanks<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你睇樣咁無計啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"587c8449b21698dbb66653ff4457d3720e5791fe","tid":498460,"uid":146205,"like":2